  ('ec0e0000-0000-5000-8000-000000000031'::uuid, 'documentation'::public.testimonial_category, 'I appreciate that this vendor lists the testing lab name directly on the COA rather than just a generic report, which makes it easier to verify independently. I''ve now ordered three different lots and all three have been within expected purity ranges of each other, so batch-to-batch consistency seems solid. Packaging includes a reusable cold pack, which is a nice detail. Only minor con is checkout doesn''t save previous order details for reordering, so you have to re-enter everything each time.', 'CoachTerry', 'Detailed COA and consistent lot quality', 'PT-141', 5, true, '2026-06-05'::date, '31', 'technical_expert', 'detailed', 'research_peptide_mock_reviews.json#id=31', '88cb6dea-f40c-5697-883b-23ae4fcff359', 30, null),
