  ('ec0e0000-0000-5000-8000-000000000037'::uuid, 'service'::public.testimonial_category, 'Second time ordering, just as smooth as the first.', 'Sarah K.', 'Will order again', 'Cagrilintide', 5, true, '2026-07-06'::date, '37', 'verified_buyer', 'short', 'research_peptide_mock_reviews.json#id=37', '16ee47f8-57b6-5c83-86a9-2104808d51d1', 36, null),
  ('ec0e0000-0000-5000-8000-000000000038'::uuid, 'service'::public.testimonial_category, 'I don''t have much technical knowledge about this product, so I mostly relied on the person I bought it for to confirm quality. From my end as the buyer, the website was easy to navigate, checkout was quick, and I received shipping updates the whole way. It arrived a day earlier than the estimate, which was a nice surprise for a gift order. The recipient said everything looked correct and was packaged properly. Would use this site again for a similar gift.', 'SisterInLaw_Deb', 'Ordered as a surprise for a family member', 'Melanotan II', 5, false, '2026-03-12'::date, '38', 'gift_giver', 'detailed', 'research_peptide_mock_reviews.json#id=38', '3ff39b4b-731b-5338-81c0-313784e6431e', 37, null),
  ('ec0e0000-0000-5000-8000-000000000039'::uuid, 'documentation'::public.testimonial_category, 'Cross-checked against a previous lot''s COA and the numbers lined up closely. Good documentation practices.', 'K.L. (PhD)', 'Consistent with prior lots', 'BPC-157', 5, true, '2026-06-13'::date, '39', 'technical_expert', 'short', 'research_peptide_mock_reviews.json#id=39', '00554dbd-5be4-5020-8817-4199f99438fa', 38, null),
  ('ec0e0000-0000-5000-8000-000000000040'::uuid, 'support'::public.testimonial_category, 'After reconstituting, the solution had a faint cloudiness that I hadn''t seen with previous orders from other vendors, which made me hesitant to trust the batch. I reached out to support with photos and it took almost four days to get a response, and the reply was fairly generic and didn''t address the cloudiness directly. Pros: shipping speed was fine and the outer packaging was intact. Cons: the quality concern combined with the slow, unhelpful response is enough that I''ll be looking elsewhere for my next order.', 'Justin C.', 'Solution looked cloudy, slow response from support', 'TB-500', 2, true, '2026-04-19'::date, '40', 'verified_buyer', 'detailed', 'research_peptide_mock_reviews.json#id=40', '359c3634-2263-5347-8c3b-622037de747d', 39, null),
